    schema:inCodeSet <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/HISCO> ;
    schema:name "Mathematician (Applied Mathematics)"@en-gb .

<https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/code/hisco/08240> a <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/MicroGroup>,
