    schema:inCodeSet <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/HISCO> ;
    schema:name "Housekeeper (Private Service)"@en-gb .

<https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/code/hisco/22440> a <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/MicroGroup>,
