    schema:inCodeSet <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/HISCO> ;
    schema:name "Supervisor and General Foreman (Mining, Quarrying and Well-Drilling)"@en-gb .

<https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/code/hisco/22630> a <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/MicroGroup>,
