        "2-26.50"^^xsd:string ;
    schema:description "Supervises production activities of a distinct unit within an establishment concerned with manufacturing and assembly of mechanical equipment and metal products, such as machinery, precision instruments and scientific apparatus, transport equipment and metal parts of various kinds, and controls and co-ordinates the activities of workers in this unit engaged in various occupations."@en ;
    schema:inCodeSet <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/HISCO> ;
    schema:name "Supervisor and General Foreman (Manufacturing of Machinery and Metal Products)"@en-gb .

<https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/code/hisco/22655> a <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/MicroGroup>,
