    schema:inCodeSet <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/HISCO> ;
    schema:name "Supervisor and General Foreman (Manufacturing and Installation of Electrical and Electronic Equipment)"@en-gb .

<https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/code/hisco/22660> a <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/MicroGroup>,
