    schema:description "Supervises production activities of a distinct unit within an establishment concerned with the fabrication of products from paper, rubber, plastics or other synthetic materials or the manufacture of pharmaceutical and chemical products, and controls and co-ordinates the activities of workers in this unit engaged in various occupations."@en ;
