    schema:codeValue 63190,
        "6-31.90"^^xsd:string ;
    schema:description "This group includes loggers not elsewhere classified, for example those who are occupied mainly in operating wood-harvesting machines to fell, branch, cross-cut or bark trees to perform other logging operations; loading logs into chutes, or stacking them preparatory to transport out of forest; shaping rough wooden products from logs, such as railway ties and telephone poles, near felling sites; examining logs and grading them according to quality or measuring them to determine their volume of marketable timber."@en ;
    schema:inCodeSet <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/HISCO> ;
    schema:name "Other Loggers"@en-gb .

<https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/code/hisco/63220> a <https://iisg.amsterdam/resource/hisco/MicroGroup>,
